Allstar Inns LP said itbegan a public offering of 5,832,037 depositary units priced at12.50 dlrs a unit through lead underwriter Drexel BurnhamLambert Inc and co-managing underwriters Dean Witter ReynoldsInc and Bateman Eichler Hill Richards.    The units represent limited partners' interest in thecompany.    Proceeds will be used to repay debt. Reuter&#3;